There is as much difference between what a positive-sum 'open quantity' =
based system offers over one which is  zero sum 'price' based as there =
is between a balance forward and an open item accounting system. For =
that matter look at the benefits of being on-line and interactive as =
opposed to being in batch mode. Sure the results can be similar but the =
structure is very different. =20

