     "A Century of Global Stock Markets"

      BY: WILLIAM N. GOETZMANN
             Yale School of Management
          PHILIPPE JORION
             University of California, Irvine

           Date:     December 1996

           Contact:  Philippe Jorion
           E-Mail:   MAILTO:PJORION@UCI.EDU
